      <h4>Organizational / Time Constraints</h4>
      <p>Riordan would like to have the new system in place before January 1, 2016. The driver to meet this date is that the licensing agreements for many of the legacy HR systems are up for renewal at that time.</p>

      <h4>Risks of Not Doing the Project</h4>
      <p>The primary risk of not implementing the new system is that the legacy systems are running on aging hardware with an increasing risk of failure. Another key risk is that the total costs associated with implementing a new system HR will only continue
        to increase over time.</p>

